title: GSX - Ground Services X full newest version
description:
Ground Services X
GSX

Installation instructions:


1. pull down your internet !! (very important)

2. install "1 - gsx_fsx_setup.exe"

3. install all vehicle update 3-6

4. open "2 - gsx serials.reg" and just press yes

5. start fsx and see if the gsx is working on any airport

6. connect to the internet

7. install "7 - gsx_fsx_setup.exe"

8. start fsx and see if the gsx is working on any airport
    if it is on demo then you need to start to number 1 in this list and when you get to number 6 do not connect to the internet
    and it should work

tested on win 7 64 bit with real KLAX and real KJFK
